title: Step Back In Time! Smith River Front Living 1595 North
text:
Step Back In Time! Smith River Front Living 1595 North ad date: 09/30/2015 
Smith River Front Living 1595 North Fork Lp, Gasquet, CA Live on the North Fork Loop in Gasquet! Live a lifestyle you have probably only dreamed of! Gasquet is a 20 minute drive to Crescent City and 45 minutes to Oregon. Home is redwood construction with numerous original features. 3 bedroom, 2 bath with large storage shed and enclosed carport. Plenty of room to garden and easy access to the river and community access to the best swimming hole on the North Fork. Needs TLC but possibilities are endless! No. 1500235 $325,000
